Achievements.Name: The Flag is Mine
Achievements.Description: Keep the flag for two straight minutes in Capture the Flag mode.

Achievements.Name: Triple Killer
Achievements.Description: Perform 3 Triple Kills in a single match.

Achievements.Name: Eyes on the Prize
Achievements.Description: Retrieve 5 Treasures in a row in Treasure Hunt mode.

Achievements.Name: F*ck Da Police
Achievements.Description: Do not get killed in a Police Chase game.

Achievements.Name: No Need No Gun
Achievements.Description: Get five kills without using your gun.

Achievements.Name: Minute Madness Expert
Achievements.Description: Get most of your kills when the Minute Madness is enabled.

Achievements.Name: A God Among Men
Achievements.Description: Win by scoring more points than all other players combined (in 3 or 4-player mode).

Achievements.Name: Possessive
Achievements.Description: Be the first one to capture the flag and never let go of it.

Achievements.Name: Souvenir Collector
Achievements.Description: Win a Dog Tag game with least kills.

Achievements.Name: Comeback is a B*tch
Achievements.Description: Be the player with fewer points at sometime and still win the game (in 3 or 4-player mode).

Achievements.Name: Serve and Protect
Achievements.Description: Kill at least one player every time you are the police in a Police Chase game.
Achieve 100% in the single player challenges.

Achievements.Name: Everybody's Dead
Achievements.Description: All players have died in a short period of time (in 4-player mode).
